column2: select PMDB..PM_F_FORMAT_DATE(O.DATA_DATE_FR, 'YYYY-MM-DD') as DATA_DATE_FR, M.RECONCILE_CODE, T.TABLE_NAME as DIFF_TABLE, DF.D_MOBILE_NO as DIFF_MOBILE_NO, PMDB..PM_F_FORMAT_DATE(DF.TRANS_DTM, 'YYYY-MM-DD') as DIFF_TRANS_DATE , DF.FACE_VALUE as DIFF_FACE_VALUE, DF.REF_ID as DIFF_REF_ID from PMDB..PM_PREPAID_BATCH_RECONCILE_DIFF DF  inner join PMDB..PM_PREPAID_BATCH_RECONCILE R on (DF.BATCH_RCC_ID = R.BATCH_RCC_ID and R.LAST_BOO = 'Y')  inner join PMDB..PM_PREPAID_LOAD_BATCH B on (R.BATCH_ID = B.BATCH_ID)  inner join PMDB..PM_RECONCILE_MAPPING M on (R.RECONCILE_ID = M.RECONCILE_ID)  inner join PMDB..PM_RECONCILE_MAPPING_TABLE T on (M.RECONCILE_ID = T.RECONCILE_ID)  inner join PMDB..PM_PREPAID_BATCH_RECONCILE_DIFF_TABLE DT on (DF.DIFF_ID = DT.DIFF_ID and T.TABLE_ID = DT.TABLE_ID) inner join PMDB..PM_JOB_ORDER O on (B.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID)  where B.ORDER_ID = @order_id
